; Regression test for issue #792: Adjustment in ledger register report with -Mn
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/792
;
; With -B -X -Mn on multi-currency transactions, spurious <Adjustment> lines
; should not appear. Cost basis (-B) should not trigger revaluations.
; Also, -Mn should collapse correctly: <Total> for multiple accounts,
; account name when only one account matches in a period.

2013/01/05 Buy groceries
    Expenses:Food     $50.00
    Assets:Cash

2013/01/20 Dining out
    Expenses:Dining   $30.00
    Assets:Cash

2013/02/05 Buy groceries
    Expenses:Food     $40.00
    Assets:Cash

2013/03/15 Foreign Expense
    Expenses:Travel     200 EUR @ $1.33
    Assets:Cash

2013/03/20 Another Foreign Expense
    Expenses:Food     100 EUR @ $1.35
    Assets:Cash

test reg -Mn Expenses
13-Jan-01 - 13-Jan-31           <Total>                      $80.00       $80.00
13-Feb-01 - 13-Feb-28           Expenses:Food                $40.00      $120.00
13-Mar-01 - 13-Mar-31           <Total>                     300 EUR      $120.00
                                                                         300 EUR
end test

test reg -B -X $ -Mn Expenses
13-Jan-01 - 13-Jan-31           <Total>                      $80.00       $80.00
13-Feb-01 - 13-Feb-28           Expenses:Food                $40.00      $120.00
13-Mar-01 - 13-Mar-31           <Total>                     $401.00      $521.00
end test
